\f1\b\fs48 VistaClock
\fs28 \
\pard\pardeftab720\ri-2149\partightenfactor0

\b0 \cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\ri-2155\partightenfactor0
\cf0 The panel shows the default configuration, calendar and one clock.  It also shows the toolbar, which can be selected from the settings button.\
